(43, 3, 25, 60, 3, 21, 21, 'purifying', 'Connection of Purification and Baptism', 'This connection highlights the theme of purification in both passages. John 3:25 discusses ''purifying,'' while 1 Peter 3:21 relates baptism to a spiritual cleansing and a good conscience.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
