(43, 3, 26, 43, 1, 7, 7, 'barest witness', 'Witness and Belief Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of bearing witness to Jesus as the Light. Both passages emphasize the role of John in directing people towards Jesus, who is baptizing and drawing all men to himself.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
