(43, 5, 20, 61, 1, 17, 17, 'the Father loveth the Son', 'Connection of Sonship and Glory', 'Both passages emphasize the relationship between the Father and the Son. John 5:20 mentions the Father''s love for the Son, while 2 Peter 1:17 highlights the honor and glory bestowed upon the Son by the Father.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
