(43, 7, 52, 2, 2, 14, 14, 'out of Galilee ariseth no prophet', 'Connection of Prophetic Origin', 'Both passages emphasize the skepticism surrounding the origins of leaders. In John, the question of a prophet''s origin from Galilee reflects a similar doubt in Exodus regarding Moses''s authority as a leader.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
