(43, 7, 53, 19, 33, 10, 10, 'every man went unto his own house', 'Divine Authority Over Human Plans', 'This connection highlights the contrast between human actions and divine sovereignty. In John 7:53, people return to their own houses, while Psalms 33:10 emphasizes that the Lord nullifies the plans of the heathen.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
