(43, 8, 40, 48, 4, 16, 16, NULL, 'Truth and Opposition', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of truth-telling leading to opposition. In John, Jesus faces hostility for revealing the truth, while in Galatians, Paul questions if he has become an enemy for doing the same.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
