(43, 8, 42, 43, 12, 49, 49, 'neither came I of myself, but he sent me', 'Connection of Divine Sending', 'Both passages emphasize that Jesus did not come of himself but was sent by the Father. This highlights the relationship between Jesus and God, underscoring His role as the messenger of God''s commands.', 'theme', 0.986, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
