(43, 9, 25, 43, 9, 30, 30, 'whereas I was blind, now I see', 'Healing and Recognition of Jesus', 'Both passages emphasize the transformation from blindness to sight, highlighting the miraculous nature of the healing. The man acknowledges his newfound ability to see and questions the ignorance of others regarding Jesus'' identity.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
