(43, 9, 28, 40, 27, 39, 39, 'reviled him', 'Reviling and Mocking in Context', 'This connection highlights the theme of reviling and mockery directed at individuals associated with faith. Both passages depict a scenario where individuals are ridiculed for their beliefs, emphasizing the hostility faced by disciples of faith.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
