(43, 9, 39, 42, 1, 79, 79, 'that they which see not might see', 'Light and Darkness Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of bringing light to those in darkness. Both passages emphasize the transformative power of Jesus, with John 9:39 focusing on sight and blindness, while Luke 1:79 speaks of guiding feet into peace.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
