(43, 10, 28, 43, 3, 15, 16, 'they shall never perish', 'Eternal Life and Perishing', 'Both passages emphasize the promise of eternal life and the assurance that believers shall not perish. The repetition of ''not perish'' in both verses highlights a central theme of salvation and security in faith.', 'theme', 0.671, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 10, 28, 58, 7, 25, 25, 'eternal life', 'Eternal Life and Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the assurance of salvation and eternal life for believers. John 10:28 speaks of eternal life and security in Christ''s hand, while Hebrews 7:25 highlights His ability to save completely and intercede for them.', 'theme', 0.657, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
