(43, 10, 28, 50, 1, 6, 6, 'eternal life', 'Eternal Security in Christ', 'This connection highlights the assurance of eternal life and God''s ongoing work in believers. Both passages emphasize the security and perseverance of those who belong to Christ.', 'theme', 0.58, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
