(43, 10, 30, 43, 1, 1, 2, 'I and my Father are one', 'Unity of Christ and God', 'Both passages emphasize the oneness of Christ with God. John 10:30 states, ''I and my Father are one,'' while John 1:1 affirms that ''the Word was God,'' highlighting the divine unity.', 'theme', 0.7689999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
