(43, 10, 32, 14, 24, 20, 22, NULL, 'Rejection of God''s Messengers', 'Both passages emphasize the rejection of God''s messengers. In John 10:32, Jesus refers to His good works, while in 2 Chronicles 24:20-22, Zechariah is stoned for delivering God''s message. This connection highlights a theme of hostility towards those sent by God.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
