(43, 10, 32, 43, 5, 19, 20, 'good works have I shewed you', 'Connection of Works and Authority', 'This connection highlights the relationship between Jesus'' works and His authority derived from the Father. Both passages emphasize that Jesus acts based on what He sees the Father do, reinforcing His claim to perform good works.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
