(43, 16, 10, 60, 3, 18, 18, 'of righteousness, because I go to my Father', 'Connection of Righteousness and Suffering', 'This connection highlights the theme of righteousness through Christ''s suffering. Both passages emphasize the role of Christ in bringing believers to God, linking His departure to the Father with His sacrificial act.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 16, 10, 24, 23, 5, 6, 'righteousness', 'Connection of Righteousness Theme', 'Both passages emphasize righteousness as a key theme. John 16:10 refers to righteousness in the context of Jesus'' departure, while Jeremiah 23:5-6 speaks of a righteous Branch who will bring salvation and justice.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
